Chronicle of the adventures of Scotland-born hero of the Revolutionary War, John Paul Jones whose exploits take him across the globe, from the West Indies to Russia and France. He was often underappreciated by the American government and was eventually assigned to protect Russia's Catherine the Great. Based on the short story "Nor'wester" by Clements Ripley.
